Your are all nuts! :)

Buy a table jack and a set of wheel ramps. That way you can use the "table"
on the table jack as a "table" when you are not using it! A ATV jack, floor
jack, transmission jack, etc are all single use specific. Table jacks are
all about multipurpose.

Chris (BustedBus) and I use these exclusively. And we have pulled, oh I lost
count at 50, motors and trannys in the last 3 years.

http://www.harborfreight.com/cpi/ctaf/displayitem.taf?Itemnumber=94822

http://www.napaonline.com/MasterPages/NOLMaster.aspx?PageId=470&LineCode=BK&
PartNumber=8201206&Description=Car+Ramps


All in good fun...

